jobDescription.text:
Job Title: Cherry Pickers
As a Cherry Picker, you will play a vital role in our operations, ensuring that our products are selected and handled with utmost care and precision. Your efforts will directly contribute to our commitment to excellence and customer satisfaction.

Location:
Preferred location Houston, TX.

Salary:
16 to 18 USD Per Hour

Roles and Responsibilities:
- Utilize cherry pickers to accurately select products from high shelves.
- Perform material handling duties with attention to safety and efficiency.
- Assemble orders and prepare them for dispatch according to company standards.
- Process incoming stock and conduct labeling and inventory management.
- Maintain a clean and organized workspace through effective housekeeping.
- Collaborate with team members to meet daily goals and ensure quality service.
- Conduct follow-up calls and assist with paperwork related to order processing.

Preferred Skills:
- FL Studio
- Freight management
- Order selecting
- Basic math skills
- Direct retail experience
- Team-focused attitude
- Warehouse management system familiarity
- Assembling and dispatching orders
- Processing incoming stock

Experience Level:
Preferred experience level is 0 to 50 years.

Employment Type:
Direct hire.

Company Description:
TRC Talent Solutions is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer (EOE). All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, sex, age, national origin, protected veteran status, disability status, sexual orientation, gender identity or expression, marital status, genetic information, or any other characteristic protected by law.

At TRC, we take pride in fulfilling our opportunity to add value to our clients business as their staffing partner, while working tirelessly to connect thousands of individuals each year with work opportunities where they can meet the needs of their families and have the potential to build their careers.
